{"id":947,"date":"2019-09-09T19:30:41","date_gmt":"2019-09-09T16:30:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/dev.atomicwallet.io\/?p=947"},"modified":"2021-06-17T16:52:46","modified_gmt":"2021-06-17T13:52:46","slug":"how-to-make-atomic-swap","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/academy\/how-to-make-atomic-swap","title":{"rendered":"Atomic Swap FAQ &#8211; Overview and How Atomic Swap Works"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"450\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"How to make atomic swap\"  class=\"wp-image-13600 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/how-to-make-atomic-swap.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/how-to-make-atomic-swap.png 300w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/how-to-make-atomic-swap.png 910w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/how-to-make-atomic-swap.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/how-to-make-atomic-swap.png 1920w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/how-to-make-atomic-swap.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/how-to-make-atomic-swap.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/how-to-make-atomic-swap.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/how-to-make-atomic-swap.png 800w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Atomic Swaps is a new technology that makes it possible to exchange cryptocurrencies directly and without third parties. For example\u200a\u2014\u200ayou can exchange BTC to LTC with the fixed and small fee for any amount without centralization exchanges.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this short Article you can see how easy you can perform Atomic Swap into Atomic Wallet.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"there-is-two-parts\">There is two parts:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>1. Create your own Swap Order<\/li><li>2. Accept existing Swap Order<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"1-create-your-own-swap-order\">1. Create your own Swap Order<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>1.1. First of all, you should click the \u201cAtomic Swap\u201d tab at the left menu. There are three tabs from above: \u201cMarkets\u201d, \u201cPlace order\u201d and \u201cMy orders\u201d. \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"598\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13612 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-1.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-1.png 270w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-1.png 685w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-1.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-1.png 1445w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-1.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-1.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-1.png 300w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-1.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-1.png 800w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>1.3. Use the arrow icon to change the trading pair. Then you have to set the amount that you want to exchange, set the trade rate and Place the order \u21e9 \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"585\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13636 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-2-1.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-2-1.png 800w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-2-1-300x219.png 300w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-2-1-768x562.png 768w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>1.4. Or you can specify variable values with \u201cAdvanced settings\u201d, other people will be able to choose how much they want to exchange. Just set the min amount you want to exchange, then other people will set the amount between min and max that is possible. Click Place order \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"588\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13648 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-3.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-3.png 275w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-3.png 697w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-3.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-3.png 1469w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-3.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-3.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-3.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-3.png 800w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>1.5. And also you can click on \u201cMarket price\u201d checkbox to set the large\/small price than the market price. You will be able to set the \u201cMargin percent\u201d to make your order more attractive to buyers. Then click Place order \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"588\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13672 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1.png 275w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1.png 697w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1.png 1469w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1.png 800w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>1.6. After that, you\u2019ll see your order in the \u201cMy orders\u201d tab. You should wait until someone will start Atomic Swap with you \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"588\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"\"  class=\"wp-image-13684 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1-1.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1-1.png 275w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1-1.png 697w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1-1.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1-1.png 1469w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1-1.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1-1.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1-1.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-4-1-1.png 800w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>1.7. When someone will start Atomic Swap with you there\u2019ll be request to you where you\u2019ll have to enter the password of your Atomic Wallet and click on \u201cStart Swap\u201d \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"599\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13696 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-6.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-6.png 800w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-6-300x225.png 300w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-6-768x575.png 768w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All the future proceed will perform Automatically and you just have to wait some time while there will be transactions confirmations at blockexplorer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"588\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13804 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-7-1.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-7-1.png 275w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-7-1.png 697w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-7-1.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-7-1.png 1469w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-7-1.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-7-1.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-7-1.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-7-1.png 800w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"2-accept-existing-swap-order\">2. Accept existing Swap Order<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>2.1. When you have chosen the Trading pair you can see below all Orders that exist at this moment. Just choose one and click the SWAP button \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"598\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13792 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-8.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-8.png 270w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-8.png 685w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-8.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-8.png 1445w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-8.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-8.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-8.png 300w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-8.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-8.png 800w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>2.2. Will open a window with Swap details, you need to enter the password of your Atomic Wallet, then send Swap request to the maker of this order and wait while maker confirms it \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"591\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13780 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-9.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-9.png 273w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-9.png 693w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-9.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-9.png 1462w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-9.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-9.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-9.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-9.png 800w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>2.3. When the maker of this order confirm your request and start the Swap you\u2019ll see the Swap process and details, there should be green all the checkboxes to complete \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"588\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13768 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-10.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-10.png 275w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-10.png 697w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-10.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-10.png 1469w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-10.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-10.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-10.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-10.png 800w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>2.4. You can close previous window and return it back by click \u201cDetails\u201d button, but you should be online and don\u2019t leave out of your wallet to complete the Swap, because it proceeds by your personal device without any third party \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"599\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13756 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-11.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-11.png 800w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-11-300x225.png 300w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-11-768x575.png 768w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>2.5. When all the checkboxes will be green then Swap is complete and your deal is Successful \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"588\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13744 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-12.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-12.png 275w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-12.png 697w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-12.png 768w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-12.png 1469w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-12.png 1536w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-12.png 2048w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-12.png 380w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-12.png 800w\" ><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>2.6. Now you can see the deal with \u201cSuccess\u201d marker in your orders \u21e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img  loading=\"lazy\"  width=\"800\"  height=\"597\"  src=\"data:image\/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABAQMAAAAl21bKAAAAA1BMVEUAAP+KeNJXAAAAAXRSTlMAQObYZgAAAAlwSFlzAAAOxAAADsQBlSsOGwAAAApJREFUCNdjYAAAAAIAAeIhvDMAAAAASUVORK5CYII=\"  alt=\"Atomic Swap FAQ\"  class=\"wp-image-13732 pk-lazyload\"  data-pk-sizes=\"auto\"  data-ls-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"  data-pk-src=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-13.png\"  data-pk-srcset=\"https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-13.png 271w, https:\/\/atomicwallet.io\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/atomic-swap-13.png 686w, https:\/\/a